snippet.title: Garbage Girl Louise - Demo Release Trailer
snippet.description:
https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/garbage-girl-louise-rebuilt-demo.2128/

What Even Is Garbage Girl Louise?
Simple! Garbage Girl Louise is an indie platformer about breaking down boxes, cleaning up streets, and taking names! Of course this is done through bouncing on evil moles, magic trash cans, and cardboard boxes, all while tossing anything you can get your grubby trash girl hands on! Save trapped raccoons, meet weirdos around the city, and even race against your ex-girlfriend!
Dingy streets! Bubble wrap*! Magical eggs! Lesbians! Yeah, we have everything!

(*There is no actual bubble wrap included with this product, though you are free to bring your own)
